00:36:42,990 --> 00:36:44,310
- I'll schedule a full staff meeting

815
00:36:44,310 --> 00:36:45,490
for early tomorrow morning.

816
00:36:45,490 --> 00:36:46,880
- Wait.

817
00:36:46,880 --> 00:36:48,690
Why wasn't I told that this laboratory

818
00:36:48,690 --> 00:36:50,760
is actually a commercial company?

819
00:36:50,760 --> 00:36:52,110
I've learned that it's an enterprise

820
00:36:52,110 --> 00:36:53,543
of Brane Pharmaceuticals.

821
00:36:54,900 --> 00:36:56,530
- To begin with, let me assure you

822
00:36:56,530 --> 00:36:58,740
that this is not a commercial enterprise.

823
00:36:58,740 --> 00:37:00,980
Brane Pharmaceuticals created this research center

824
00:37:00,980 --> 00:37:02,480
purely as a public service.

825
00:37:02,480 --> 00:37:05,363
It's a multimillion dollar act of humanitarianism.

826
00:37:09,900 --> 00:37:13,290
- You have an elegant hypothyrosis but it can not be proven.

827
00:37:13,290 --> 00:37:15,800
Such an examination would require surgery,

828
00:37:15,800 --> 00:37:18,960
brainstem surgery where one slit means death.

829
00:37:18,960 --> 00:37:21,120
- Yes, we're very fortune to have Dr. Black Jack

830
00:37:21,120 --> 00:37:23,060
here with us to perform the surgery.

831
00:37:23,060 --> 00:37:24,760
- Had the patient been selected?

832
00:37:24,760 --> 00:37:26,240
If not, are you open to entertain

833
00:37:26,240 --> 00:37:28,093
any recommendations we might suggest?

834
00:37:29,228 --> 00:37:31,961
(somber beat music)

835
00:37:31,961 --> 00:37:35,128
(cafeteria commotion)

836
00:37:39,530 --> 00:37:41,910
- Well, Dr. Black Jack, I see you've scheduled your surgery

837
00:37:41,910 --> 00:37:43,160
for tomorrow morning at eight.

838
00:37:43,160 --> 00:37:45,170
The patient will be Nicholas Doris, won't it?

839
00:37:45,170 --> 00:37:47,170
- [Black Jack] Yes, that's right.

840
00:37:47,170 --> 00:37:48,003
- I think you better look

841
00:37:48,003 --> 00:37:50,070
at this computer disk immediately, Black Jack.

842
00:37:51,480 --> 00:37:53,919
(wind howling)

843
00:37:53,919 --> 00:37:57,336
(construction commotion)

844
00:38:04,403 --> 00:38:07,070
(phone ringing)

845
00:38:14,152 --> 00:38:14,990
[Jo] This is Jo Brane.

846
00:38:14,990 --> 00:38:17,160
Shut down the operation.

847
00:38:17,160 --> 00:38:17,993
- What?

848
00:38:17,993 --> 00:38:19,490
You can't be serious, Miss Brane.

849
00:38:19,490 --> 00:38:21,300
- Keep a skeleton crew on hand for maintenance.

850
00:38:21,300 --> 00:38:23,220
Send everybody else home.

851
00:38:23,220 --> 00:38:26,750
Repeating my order, shut down the refinery at once.

852
00:38:26,750 --> 00:38:29,799
And I want everyone out by the end of the day, understood?

853
00:38:29,799 --> 00:38:31,040
- [Worker] Yes, ma'am.

854
00:38:31,040 --> 00:38:32,700
When can we reopen?

855
00:38:32,700 --> 00:38:34,740
- I'm afraid I'll have to let you know later.

856
00:38:34,740 --> 00:38:37,564
It could be anywhere from a month to a half a year.

857
00:38:37,564 --> 00:38:40,147
(horn blowing)

858
00:38:41,000 --> 00:38:43,730
- [Announcer] Attention, stop all work immediately!

859
00:38:43,730 --> 00:38:46,963
I repeat, stop all work immediately!

860
00:38:46,963 --> 00:38:50,028
(ominous music)

861
00:38:50,028 --> 00:38:52,611
(wind howling)

862
00:38:58,138 --> 00:39:00,805
(steam hissing)

863
00:39:05,098 --> 00:39:07,300
- Hotter, hotter,

864
00:39:07,300 --> 00:39:08,661
much hotter.

865
00:39:08,661 --> 00:39:11,411
(pleasant music)

866
00:39:24,500 --> 00:39:27,460
- Hello, Mr. Doris, can you hear me?

867
00:39:27,460 --> 00:39:30,200
I'm Dr. Black Jack, I'll be your surgeon.

868
00:39:30,200 --> 00:39:31,930
- Will I ever be able to participate

869
00:39:31,930 --> 00:39:33,433
in track and field again?

870
00:39:34,560 --> 00:39:36,240
You're looking at the world record holder

871
00:39:36,240 --> 00:39:37,680
in the pole vaulting event

872
00:39:37,680 --> 00:39:40,150
but now I can't even hold the pole in my grip.

873
00:39:40,150 --> 00:39:42,260
I soared through the air like an eagle!

874
00:39:42,260 --> 00:39:43,800
I once cleared seven meters

875
00:39:43,800 --> 00:39:46,670
and now I can't get out of bed without assistance!

876
00:39:46,670 --> 00:39:48,530
What a cruel joke.

877
00:39:48,530 --> 00:39:50,940
I've gone through seven major surgeries.

878
00:39:50,940 --> 00:39:53,200
What am I, some kind of guinea pig?

879
00:39:53,200 --> 00:39:55,520
- I understood you volunteered for this operation.

880
00:39:55,520 --> 00:39:56,640
Was I wrong?

881
00:39:56,640 --> 00:39:58,060
- No, that's right.

882
00:39:58,060 --> 00:40:00,920
But I did negotiate a few stipulations.

883
00:40:00,920 --> 00:40:02,830
If you discover I can't be cured,

884
00:40:02,830 --> 00:40:05,310
I want you to erase my memory.

885
00:40:05,310 --> 00:40:06,680
If I can forget what I was,

886
00:40:06,680 --> 00:40:09,706
it might be easier for me to accept what I've become.

887
00:40:09,706 --> 00:40:12,405
(laughing)

888
00:40:12,405 --> 00:40:14,500
- You also stipulated that your family

889
00:40:14,500 --> 00:40:15,650
is not to be notified.

890
00:40:15,650 --> 00:40:17,330
Do you mind telling me why?

891
00:40:17,330 --> 00:40:18,770
- I don't want them to see me.

892
00:40:18,770 --> 00:40:21,550
This is not how I want to be remembered.

893
00:40:21,550 --> 00:40:24,740
Back home, they put up a statue to remember me by.

894
00:40:24,740 --> 00:40:26,793
That's how I want them to think of me.

895
00:40:28,119 --> 00:40:30,869
(water rumbling)

896
00:40:31,850 --> 00:40:33,120
- By the way, Black Jack,

897
00:40:33,120 --> 00:40:35,000
have you looked at that computer disk I gave you?

898
00:40:35,000 --> 00:40:36,770
- I'll take a look at it now.

899
00:40:36,770 --> 00:40:39,520
(birds flapping)

900
00:40:43,551 --> 00:40:45,671
(computer chiming)

901
00:40:45,671 --> 00:40:48,171
(saw buzzing)

902
00:40:56,552 --> 00:40:59,469
(computer beeping)

903
00:41:01,010 --> 00:41:01,890
- What are you doing?

904
00:41:01,890 --> 00:41:04,598
The trauma will cause the patient to stop breathing!

905
00:41:04,598 --> 00:41:07,515
(flatline beeping)

906
00:41:09,480 --> 00:41:10,460
- I've failed again!

907
00:41:10,460 --> 00:41:12,880
This is insane, it can't be done!

908
00:41:12,880 --> 00:41:15,520
- [Jo] Prepare the next patient immediately in OR-5.

909
00:41:15,520 --> 00:41:16,353
- Yes, ma'am.

910
00:41:16,353 --> 00:41:17,850
- Will not do this any longer!

911
00:41:17,850 --> 00:41:21,230
Experimenting on human beings is inexcusable!

912
00:41:21,230 --> 00:41:22,680
- You will continue.

913
00:41:22,680 --> 00:41:24,590
The information we need can only be obtained

914
00:41:24,590 --> 00:41:26,271
through living specimens.

915
00:41:26,271 --> 00:41:28,940
(foreboding music)

916
00:41:28,940 --> 00:41:30,370
- [Jack Voiceover] The data disc Eric had lifted

917
00:41:30,370 --> 00:41:32,060
from the project's top secret files

918
00:41:32,060 --> 00:41:35,800
laid bare a horrifying history, one failure after another.

919
00:41:35,800 --> 00:41:38,100
Presumably, these were the super humans

920
00:41:38,100 --> 00:41:40,810
whose names had been dropped from the original lists

921
00:41:40,810 --> 00:41:43,020
and whose medical records were no longer on file

922
00:41:43,020 --> 00:41:44,781
at the research center.

923
00:41:44,781 --> 00:41:47,698
(foreboding music)

924
00:41:58,242 --> 00:42:00,825
(rain pouring)

925
00:42:04,007 --> 00:42:07,621
(engine rumbling)

926
00:42:07,621 --> 00:42:10,482
(helicopter buzzing)

927
00:42:10,482 --> 00:42:13,399
(tires screeching)

928
00:42:14,594 --> 00:42:16,739
(groaning)

929
00:42:16,739 --> 00:42:19,489
(siren alarming)

930
00:42:21,130 --> 00:42:23,180
- Do as your told and you won't get hurt!

931
00:42:24,020 --> 00:42:26,970
- Security monitor, what's going on out there?

932
00:42:26,970 --> 00:42:28,780
- This is the MSJ, Miss Brane.

933
00:42:28,780 --> 00:42:30,700
We're assuming possession of this research center

934
00:42:30,700 --> 00:42:32,040
on behalf of human rights!

935
00:42:32,040 --> 00:42:33,440
Do not attempt to resist us!

936
00:42:34,841 --> 00:42:36,872
(thudding)

937
00:42:36,872 --> 00:42:39,670
(rain pouring)

938
00:42:39,670 --> 00:42:41,550
- Did you find that computer disc interesting,

939
00:42:41,550 --> 00:42:42,383
Dr. Black jack?

940
00:42:42,383 --> 00:42:45,050
(gasping)

941
00:42:45,050 --> 00:42:46,840
I represent the MSJ.

942
00:42:46,840 --> 00:42:47,940
We're defenders of the weak,

943
00:42:47,940 --> 00:42:49,334
whose rights are being violated.

944
00:42:49,334 --> 00:42:52,540
We take action against the abuses of cooperate power.

945
00:42:52,540 --> 00:42:54,110
We have vowed to destroy corruption

946
00:42:54,110 --> 00:42:57,083
and restore human dignity and decency to our society.

947
00:42:59,040 --> 00:43:01,360
- Arrest the person in charge here.

948
00:43:01,360 --> 00:43:03,637
Her name is Jo Carol Brane.

949
00:43:03,637 --> 00:43:06,300
(suspenseful music)

950
00:43:06,300 --> 00:43:07,133
- We have to hurry.

951
00:43:07,133 --> 00:43:09,020
These guys mean business.

952
00:43:09,020 --> 00:43:09,853
- Don't move!

953
00:43:09,853 --> 00:43:11,377
Hold it right there!

954
00:43:11,377 --> 00:43:12,373
(suspenseful music)

955
00:43:12,373 --> 00:43:13,573
(thudding)

956
00:43:13,573 --> 00:43:15,823
(groaning)

957
00:43:16,817 --> 00:43:19,400
(wind howling)

958
00:43:26,222 --> 00:43:28,972
(water bubbling)

959
00:43:29,960 --> 00:43:32,658
- Attention doctors, nurses, technicians.

960
00:43:32,658 --> 00:43:36,040
Attention all employees of of St. Joe Research Center.

961
00:43:36,040 --> 00:43:38,010
This project is now under the control,

962
00:43:38,010 --> 00:43:40,030
command and protection of the MSJ.

963
00:43:40,030 --> 00:43:42,120
There's no cause for alarm.

964
00:43:42,120 --> 00:43:44,810
Our purpose is to put an end to the illegal and immoral

965
00:43:44,810 --> 00:43:47,260
procedures that were being practiced here.

966
00:43:47,260 --> 00:43:50,000
Many of you are sympathetic to our cause.

967
00:43:50,000 --> 00:43:52,410
We will welcome your cooperation in helping us

968
00:43:52,410 --> 00:43:54,000
to restore the medical integrity

969
00:43:54,000 --> 00:43:56,140
of the center and its staff.

970
00:43:56,140 --> 00:43:58,280
Those of you who chose not to cooperate

971
00:43:58,280 --> 00:44:00,610
will be held in protective custody.

972
00:44:00,610 --> 00:44:02,610
No one will be harmed.

973
00:44:02,610 --> 00:44:05,960
This will be a temporary measure but until further notice,

974
00:44:05,960 --> 00:44:07,890
all activities here will be conducted

975
00:44:07,890 --> 00:44:10,620
under strict MSJ supervision.

976
00:44:10,620 --> 00:44:11,563
That is all.

977
00:44:13,130 --> 00:44:14,710
- So, Dr. Black Jack,

978
00:44:14,710 --> 00:44:16,750
now that you've seen the Brane Company's secret files,

979
00:44:16,750 --> 00:44:19,130
may we assume your support and cooperation?

980
00:44:19,130 --> 00:44:21,090
I'm sure you must be sympathetic with our aims

981
00:44:21,090 --> 00:44:23,561
and we could certainly use your help.

982
00:44:23,561 --> 00:44:26,311
(city commotion)

983
00:44:28,000 --> 00:44:28,833
- Jo Carol,

984
00:44:28,833 --> 00:44:29,666
7-1-0-1.

985
00:44:31,569 --> 00:44:33,560
Despite having warned you about the MSJ,

986
00:44:33,560 --> 00:44:36,020
you did not take proper precautions.

987
00:44:36,020 --> 00:44:37,480
- I thought I had already prepared

988
00:44:37,480 --> 00:44:39,230
for the worst possible case scenario

989
00:44:39,230 --> 00:44:42,220
by having the refinery shut down temporarily.

990
00:44:42,220 --> 00:44:43,480
- According to my sources,

991
00:44:43,480 --> 00:44:45,810
it turned out there were quite a few MSJ members

992
00:44:45,810 --> 00:44:47,630
among that blue ribbon staff that you hired.

993
00:44:47,630 --> 00:44:49,790
- My security force could've prevented the takeover

994
00:44:49,790 --> 00:44:52,520
if the National Guard hadn't become involved.

995
00:44:52,520 --> 00:44:54,470
Try pressuring the Governor into calling them off

996
00:44:54,470 --> 00:44:56,160
if you really wanna help us.

997
00:44:56,160 --> 00:44:58,060
- The troops are there to prevent escape!

998
00:44:58,060 --> 00:45:00,480
It's a standoff with hostages involved!

999
00:45:00,480 --> 00:45:03,264
If the MSJ discovers the real truth behind your project,

1000
00:45:03,264 --> 00:45:04,793
they can destroy us!

1001
00:45:04,793 --> 00:45:07,310
- They don't have enough information to figure it out

1002
00:45:07,310 --> 00:45:10,530
and they'll never find enough evidence to prove anything.

1003
00:45:10,530 --> 00:45:12,750
- You're relieved of duty, 7-1-0-1,

1004
00:45:12,750 --> 00:45:15,312
and I'm shelving your project indefinitely.

1005
00:45:15,312 --> 00:45:17,690
(helicopter whooshing)

1006
00:45:17,690 --> 00:45:19,590
I can't say it any plainer, Jo Carol.

1007
00:45:19,590 --> 00:45:20,820
You're fired!

1008
00:45:20,820 --> 00:45:22,489
And I just hope I'll be able to cover up

1009
00:45:22,489 --> 00:45:25,273
the disgraceful debacle you're leaving me stuck with!

1010
00:45:25,273 --> 00:45:27,940
(ominous music)

1011
00:45:30,460 --> 00:45:33,020
- This is Thomas Johnston, one of MSJ's leaders.

1012
00:45:33,020 --> 00:45:35,180
He heads the North America region.

1013
00:45:35,180 --> 00:45:36,950
- My specialty psychoanalysis.

1014
00:45:36,950 --> 00:45:39,150
I own a private clinic in Vancouver.

1015
00:45:39,150 --> 00:45:40,370
- Can we do this quickly?

1016
00:45:40,370 --> 00:45:42,960
I'm scheduled to preform surgery at eight o'clock.

1017
00:45:42,960 --> 00:45:44,550
- [Thomas] I understand, doctor.

1018
00:45:44,550 --> 00:45:47,550
If I'm not mistaken, that's Nicholas Doris' CT.

1019
00:45:47,550 --> 00:45:48,383
Am I correct?

1020
00:45:48,383 --> 00:45:49,216
- [Black Jack] That's right.

1021
00:45:49,216 --> 00:45:51,876
- Nicholas is vitally important to our cause, doctor.

1022
00:45:51,876 --> 00:45:55,910
Brane Pharmaceutical's franchises 400 hospitals worldwide.

1023
00:45:55,910 --> 00:45:57,700
We've investigated their records.

1024
00:45:57,700 --> 00:45:59,960
Every single victim of full-blown Moira disease

1025
00:45:59,960 --> 00:46:01,560
turns out to have been a former patient

1026
00:46:01,560 --> 00:46:04,230
at one of Brane's hospitals within the past five years.

1027
00:46:04,230 --> 00:46:05,470
There's got to be a connection

1028
00:46:05,470 --> 00:46:08,190
but none of the patients will talk about it.

1029
00:46:08,190 --> 00:46:09,400
- They wouldn't?

1030
00:46:09,400 --> 00:46:10,880
- Not one of them.

1031
00:46:10,880 --> 00:46:12,950
All of them received some sort of procedure

1032
00:46:12,950 --> 00:46:14,490
at one of Brane's hospitals.

1033
00:46:14,490 --> 00:46:17,740
All of them subsequently developed super human abilities.

1034
00:46:17,740 --> 00:46:20,353
Eventually, then, all of them fell victim to Moira.

1035
00:46:21,270 --> 00:46:24,210
We've go to find out what they did to these people, doctor.

1036
00:46:24,210 --> 00:46:26,730
But until one of these patients is willing to testify,

1037
00:46:26,730 --> 00:46:28,880
the World Health Tribunal can't do a thing.

1038
00:46:30,040 --> 00:46:31,780
We think Nicholas might cooperate

1039
00:46:31,780 --> 00:46:34,630
but the surgery you're planning is very risky.

1040
00:46:34,630 --> 00:46:37,600
None of the other patients would even let us interview them.

1041
00:46:37,600 --> 00:46:38,760
But we believe they'll all open up

1042
00:46:38,760 --> 00:46:41,253
if we can just get Nicholas to step forward.

1043
00:46:42,470 --> 00:46:44,980
Nick's testimony is extremely important.

1044
00:46:44,980 --> 00:46:47,130
- The man's life it what's important to me.

1045
00:46:48,550 --> 00:46:49,620
Let's get to work.

1046
00:46:49,620 --> 00:46:50,605
- [Betty] Yes, doctor.

1047
00:46:50,605 --> 00:46:52,229
- [Eric] Yes, sir.

1048
00:46:52,229 --> 00:46:54,979
(engine revving)

1049
00:46:59,320 --> 00:47:00,280
- Are you there, Fendy?

1050
00:47:00,280 --> 00:47:01,590
- [Fendy] Yes, ma'am.

1051
00:47:01,590 --> 00:47:03,453
- You ready to move out, right away?

1052
00:47:04,310 --> 00:47:05,380
- I stay ready.

1053
00:47:05,380 --> 00:47:07,090
Just give the word.

1054
00:47:07,090 --> 00:47:07,923
- Wrong!

1055
00:47:07,923 --> 00:47:10,090
- I made reservations for you on the last flight tonight.

1056
00:47:10,090 --> 00:47:12,030
You can pick up the tickets at the airport.

1057
00:47:12,030 --> 00:47:13,562
- [Finny] Will you be there, ma'am?

1058
00:47:13,562 --> 00:47:14,680
(Pinoko giggling)

1059
00:47:14,680 --> 00:47:16,750
- I still have some thing to do, so I'll join you later.

1060
00:47:16,750 --> 00:47:19,488
Just make sure you get a room with a view.

1061
00:47:19,488 --> 00:47:22,757
- [Pinoko] And it is finished!

1062
00:47:22,757 --> 00:47:24,788
(tires screeching)

1063
00:47:24,788 --> 00:47:27,788
(suspenseful music)

1064
00:47:29,028 --> 00:47:30,335
(gunshots booming)

1065
00:47:30,335 --> 00:47:33,477
(tires screeching)

1066
00:47:33,477 --> 00:47:35,810
(splashing)

1067
00:47:37,155 --> 00:47:40,155
(suspenseful music)

1068
00:47:44,971 --> 00:47:47,638
(phone ringing)

1069
00:47:50,565 --> 00:47:53,898
(heart monitor beeping)

1070
00:48:06,980 --> 00:48:09,180
- How's the brainwave reading?

1071
00:48:09,180 --> 00:48:11,090
- Brainwave is normal, doctor.

1072
00:48:11,090 --> 00:48:13,640
- [Jack Voiceover] Those experiments were concentrated here,

1073
00:48:13,640 --> 00:48:17,450
between the peripheral hypothalamus and pituitary gland.

1074
00:48:17,450 --> 00:48:19,050
If we're going to find any evidence,

1075
00:48:19,050 --> 00:48:21,640
this is the most likely place for it.

1076
00:48:21,640 --> 00:48:24,080
No reputable surgeon would risk taking a scalpel

1077
00:48:24,080 --> 00:48:26,190
anywhere near the pituitary gland,

1078
00:48:26,190 --> 00:48:29,300
unless he had absolute proof of a tumor lesion.

